content.comment:
Dear reviewer, thank you for getting back to us. We integrated your recommendations as follows: We 
- updated the title to "A teacher-student framework to distill future trajectories";
- removed all mentions of the word "interpret" and now only use "extract information from trajectories" and "distill into target activations";
- clarified the use of the term "distill" in the first page;
- updated every plot and mention of the algorithm, that we now call "LDT" for Learning to Distill Trajectories.

Thanks again for helping us improve the clarity of the paper!

